<br>
<p><h5><strong>To have this app on your phone:  For iOS users:  On Safari, click the share button on the bottom middle portion of the browser, then select Add To Home Screen</strong></h5></p>
<p><h5><strong>For Android users:  Once the app has loaded, click on the add to homescreen shortcut on Firefox, or click on menu dots, then Add to homescreen for Chrome</strong></h5></p>
